text: Gemma Chan (born 29 November 1982) is an English actress. She is known for her role as Astrid in the 2018 movie Crazy Rich Asians and as Anita/Mia on the television drama Humans. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:English stage actors Category:Actors from London
